high_descs: Turn left, walk pass the sofa, turn left, walk to the end, turn left, walk to the sofa with a box on it
Grab the box on the sofa

turn on the lamp on the table

high_descs: Turn left and walk past the red couch on your left then turn left and walk until you're about one foot from the laptop then turn left and walk to the couch.
Pick up the cardboard box that's on the couch.
Turn around and walk to the fireplace then turn right and walk to the small black table that's to the right of the fireplace and turn left to face it.
Turn on the light on the small black table.

high_descs: Turn left, walk straight to the window, turn right when you reach the window, walk straight to the small stand, turn left when you reach the small stand and walk straight to the couch.
Pick up the empty box on the couch.
Turn around to face the fireplace, walk straight to the fireplace, turn right when you reach the fireplace, walk straight to the big table and turn left to face the smaller table.
Turn on the lamp on the smaller table.
anns.task_desc: Turn on the lamp with an empty box in hand.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the box on the red sofa to the left of the TV.
Pick up the box from the sofa.
Turn around and walk to the black table to the left of the window.
Turn on the lamp on the black table.
